{"type":"answer","id":47592,"parentType":"question","parentId":8023,"uid":10677,"contents":"曾经的我总是喜欢幻想那些不切实际的东西，在<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">虚拟世界</a>里放纵。但<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">回到现实</a>后才发现自己又虚度了一天，或许<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E5%B0%86%E6%9D%A5&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">将来</a>我们并不会实现自己的<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E6%A2%A6%E6%83%B3&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">梦想</a>，但我们不能够任意放肆，还有很多的事等着我们去做，很多的人等着我们去照顾，梦想太难了，换一个就好了，并不是所有的<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E6%A2%A6%E9%83%BD&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">梦都</a>要实现，梦想只是让我们有了追求，奔向<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">精神</a>上的乌托邦。 人活着就是为了自己开心，让<a href=\"http://www.so.com/s?q=%E8%BA%AB%E8%BE%B9%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;src=internal_wenda_recommend_textn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">身边的人</a>开心就够了。","date":"2019-09-04","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}